<p>This module replaces the image area and gallery area on the existing product pages.  "Deep Zoom" images are created when saving the product or if the image does not exist in Front Office (activated in admin, disabled by default)  The module also has 2 widgets - Displays the image product - Viewing the gallery product with a system of forward / backward</p>
